xfstt - X11 Font Server for TrueType fonts

This server will allow X11 applications using X core fonts to use
TrueType fonts, which are generally regarded to be the best scalable
fonts for low resolution devices like displays.


Releases
--------

  <http://download.berlios.de/xfstt/>


